room_title: Escape room "Queen City Bank Heist" by Exit Strategy in Charlotte
room_address: 4215 Stuart Andrew Blvd Ste B, Charlotte NC 28217
room_description: When you are unwillingly kidnapped by the criminal mastermind Leviathan, the mission which he bestows is a matter of life and death. Are you skilled enough to crack the Queen City Bank’s state of the art security system and steal a priceless jewel, or will Leviathan’s plan prove to be too difficult - and you perish inside?
